cmdHelpGiveawayGcreate:
```css
Creates a new giveaway in the given channel. 
Duration can be set in d (days), h (hours) or m (minutes) example: 10d 
specify the amount of winners (minimum 1) 
Write the price description within the [] brackets (emojis allowed)```
cmdHelpGiveawayGdelete: ```css\nDeletes a giveaway by a provided message URL to the respective giveaway```\n
cmdHelpGiveawayGedit:
```css
Edits a giveaway by a provided message URL to the respective giveaway.
Choose what you want to edit. Available options: duration, winners, prize
The new duration of the giveaway can be provided in m (minutes), h (hours), or d (days). Example: 10d
The new prize description needs to be written within [] brackets. Emojis allowed.```
